Create a block called mycarousel.

It is a container block with repeating child items.

Parent config fields:
- layoutVariant: select with options Grid (grid), Carousel Peek (carousel-peek), 
  Carousel Side (carousel-side). Default: carousel-peek
- autoplay: boolean toggle. Default: false
- interval: number, min 1 max 20, default 5. Label: "Interval (seconds)"
- pauseOnHover: boolean. Default: true. Label: "Pause on Hover"
- infiniteLoop: boolean. Default: false. Label: "Infinite Loop"
- sectionTitle: text
- sectionContent: richtext
- backgroundImage: reference. Label: "Section Background Image"

Child item name: mycarousel-item
Child fields:
- media: reference, required. Label: "Media (Image or Video)"
- mediaType: select with options Image (image), Video (video). Default: image
- caption: text. Label: "Caption"
- description: richtext
- ctaLabel: text. Label: "CTA Label"
- ctaUrl: aem-content, rootPath: /content/tatapower. Label: "CTA URL"

Conditional fields:
- autoplay should only show when layoutVariant is carousel-peek OR carousel-side
- interval should only show when autoplay is true
- pauseOnHover should only show when autoplay is true
- infiniteLoop should only show when layoutVariant is carousel-peek OR carousel-side

Use init_block first, then build step by step.
Do NOT create any files directly.
Use session tools only and call preview_session before generate_block.
